presses (a forced-choice experimental design).  What code do I use to 
stop the script from running until it receives a key press (f and j 
key presses being used)?

Here is sample script code for first two items:

<ep> f3  t3000 <dwc 255255255> <bc 000000000> <id keyboard> d -1 <mnr 
+f> <mpr +j> <nfb> <rcot> <cr> <eop>  

0  <ln -1>”Press YELLOW if you see 1 jumping, GREEN if you see 3 
moving”;


